Recommends: mailutils, default-mta | mail-transport-agent
Suggests: nginx | apache2
Description: ActivityPub relay with native service and resource monitoring
 Activity-Relay forwards public ActivityPub activities between subscribed
 servers. This package provides the relay server and worker, an isolated Redis
 service, resource alerts, a generated landing site, and opt-in web-server
 examples.
